  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个预约系统的状态流转图。用户从EMR同步模块进来，先创建一个草稿状态的预约，然后提交后进入待审核。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "Draft",
        "Pending"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Draft到Pending是用户提交触发的。那Pending之后呢？管理员审核通过应该到Confirmed状态吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Confirmed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Pending可以分支到Confirmed，也可以被管理员拒绝到Rejected。另外，Pending状态需要加一个备注说明会发邮件通知用户和管理员。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Confirmed",
        "Rejected",
        "email"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Pending分支和备注都加上了。Confirmed之后呢？用户到场签到应该进入服务中状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Confirmed",
        "InProgress",
        "check"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Confirmed可以走到InProgress，条件是到达开始时间且用户签到。但Confirmed也有其他分支：用户可以提前取消到Cancelled，或者超时未签到变成NoShow。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Confirmed",
        "InProgress",
        "Cancelled",
        "NoShow",
        "start"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "InProgress状态需要备注说明锁定资源吗？另外InProgress结束后应该到Completed？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "resources",
        "Completed",
        "end"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，加一下资源锁定的备注。InProgress可以到Completed，也可以紧急取消到Cancelled。最后各终态要连回不同的系统模块：Completed回EMR同步，Cancelled去诊断引擎，Rejected到患者记录，NoShow进HIPAA保险库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "Completed",
        "Cancelled",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "emergency"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
